✅ 1. Short & Simple Description

A clean and easy-to-use To-Do app designed to help you stay organised and productive. Add tasks, mark them as complete, and remove them instantly — all in a smooth, interactive interface.

✅ 2. Medium (For Portfolio / GitHub)

This To-Do application is a stylish and functional task manager built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Users can easily add new tasks, mark tasks as completed with a visual check animation, and delete items using a simple “X” button. The app saves your daily tasks, enhances productivity, and provides a smooth UI experience with a responsive design and subtle animations.

✅ 3. Professional Description (For LinkedIn / Resume / Portfolio)                            
      
A dynamic and interactive To-Do List application developed using modern front-end technologies (HTML, CSS, JavaScript). 
The app enables users to create, update, and delete tasks efficiently, providing real-time visual feedback through animations and state toggling. Features include a responsive UI, task completion toggle with check/uncheck icons, animated headings, and intuitive UX design. Built as a productivity tool to demonstrate DOM manipulation, event handling, and clean component-based UI styling.    
